data.description: Great 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in the highly desirable subdivision of Butterfield Meadows. Beautiful cabinetry throughout this lovely, custom home complimenting the gorgeous granite counters! Wood looking ceramic tile throughout the main living area, kitchen & bathrooms, with carpet in the bedrooms. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, two tier breakfast island, corner pantry & open to the living room & dining area. The large owner's bedroom features trey ceilings with plenty of natural light, an ensuite with custom built-ins, walk-in shower, & large vanity with dual sinks. Spacious guest rooms with great closets! Laundry room has built in storage. Enjoy entertaining this fall on your covered back patio with tongue & groove ceiling, privacy fence, and room for a garden, pool, playset, shed, the list is endless! Save on your home owners insurance with the new Class 4 roof! Close to Dyess, shopping and dining!
